ord count requirements.\", \"Rubrics consistently include the specific role title despite instructions to avoid it.\"]|c8ff19dfec325e8b700aa82285026e3019a896fa|7936bd65c41b9b1b7f2bfe6aef1b121639f474dc|Graphic Designer|185|84fcaed4efb510f5518998c1f00076e8d3794881|gemini-3-flash-preview|1.0|2026-02-20T16:41:12.651456Z
